commits.message:

commits.author: Daphne Gold

commits.message:
Upgrade webpack from 5.101.1 to 5.101.3 (#956)

Co-authored-by: snyk-bot <snyk-bot@snyk.io>
commits.author: decause-gov

commits.message:
Create `format_string` helper to coalesce report fields to "N/A" (#955)

Although this seems a bit pointless, perhaps, this method coalesces a
blank string into "N/A" - a common pattern within the report.
commits.author: Tom Dooner

commits.message:
FFS-3368: Add agency_partner_metadata to Tokenized API response (#954)

* Use `wrap_parameters` so Rails doesn't duplicate all the params into
  an `invitations` top-level object.
* Delete `client_agency_id` since we determine it from the API key.
* Remove three unused indexing fields for LA (first_name, middle_name,
  last_name)

Co-Authored-By: Ben Calegari <bencalegari@navapbc.com>
commits.author: Tom Dooner

commits.message:
FFS-3369: Create "doc_id" indexing field for LA (#952)

LA LDH will send us this field via the Tokenized Link API only. I tested
locally that the Generic Link flow is unaffected.
commits.author: Tom Dooner
